## Scripts

This directory contains a number of scripts useful while working on the service.

## Load testing

To run the included load testing scripts, use the [k6](https://k6.io) load testing tool.

```
# simulate a single user
k6 run --vus 1 --duration 30s load-test.js
# simulate 50 concurrent users
k6 run --vus 50 --duration 30s load-test.js
```